Host leaf*
    User root

Host *
    User metal
    IdentityFile files/ssh/id_ed25519
    IdentitiesOnly yes
    PasswordAuthentication no
    StrictHostKeyChecking no
    UserKnownHostsFile /dev/null

Host fe80::*
    ProxyCommand ssh -q -F files/ssh/config leaf01 'bash -c "exec 3<>/dev/tcp/%h/%p; cat<&0 >&3 & cat<&3 >&1"'
